--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Requirements
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Which programs and libraries are needed?
(In parantheses: versions this program was created/tested with)

 * Python 3.x
 * pillow (fork of the Python Image Library PIL)
 * LibreOffice (table osmLatLon.ods)

